cdata.name: Oceanlab
cdata.desc:
Oceanlab will act as the missing link between transactions and people, users will be able to read the blockchain as if they were reading a newspaper, accessing information related to trading, new uses of the blockchain, new technologies, projects, without browsing through an enormous amount of data.

Oceanlab is in the process of creating the technology able to gather and process an enormous, ever growing amount of data and they plan to make the tools to make that technology available to everyone.
